NEGATIVE <1:10 BY IFA.  INTERPRETATION: RESULTS INDICATIVE OF PAST EBV INFECTION.  In most populations, 90% of adults have been infected at sometime with EBV and will have measurable VCA IgG and EBNA antibodies.
